*   **Canvas (`#0B0C15`)**: Very dark. Absorbs the "infinite space" of the board.
*   **Cards (`#1C1D29`)**: Significantly lighter (Luminance ~11%) than canvas. This creates natural depth without needing heavy drop shadows, which can look muddy in dark mode.
*   **Panels (`#13141F`)**: Sit between canvas and cards.

#### 2. Text Hierarchy & Readability
*   **Primary (`#F0F1F7`)**: Avoid pure white (`#FFFFFF`). Pure white on dark causes "halation" (blurring/vibration). 94-96% white is sharper.
